title: Loop through csv files in folder and perform spatial intersect.
detail: Though I have seen similar questions here about looping through and performing operations on csv files within a directory, the code I have written for my particular case is not working. I have ~100 csv files in a directory, which are spatial datasets (all have identical columns including lat/lon coordinates and other data, but different number of rows). I am trying to clip each of them using a bounding box. Here is what I have so far:
